data.title: Galerie Paul Maenz Koln Records
data.text:
Grazia Gunn, Australian National Gallery, Canberra (see "A" for correspondence dated prior to 1984)

Scope and Contents note

10 items regarding possible acquisitions.

"Master Works of Conceptual Art," 11 Okt/19 Nov: "Anselm Kiefer," 25 Nov/23 Dec, Paul Maenz (two announcements on same poster).

"Arte Cifra" 21.6 - 21.7.79, Paul Maenz (printed texts on verso by Celant).

"Haackes Manet-Projekt '74," 4-30 July, 1974, Paul Maenz (reproductions of Haacke correspondence with Dr. Horst Keller, director of Wallraf-Richartz-Museums).

"Journey to the Surface of the Earth: Manual and Atlas," Mark Boyle.

"Robert Barry and the Art Cologne Wall Piece" at the Fair 10-16 Nov and "Francesco Clemente, Neue Arbeiten New York" at the Gallery 11 Nov - Dec 23 (two announcements on same poster)

"New York New," 5.6.-31.7.87.
